ansferred to the next flight to Nairobi but was later told he was unable to board because security wanted to talk with him after discovering the plane had lost contact March 17, 2019 In "Aviation" One of the greatest benefits of the investments by Governor  Nyesom  Ezenwo Wike  in the  security  of  lives and property ,  is the increased inflow of local and foreign investments.  Today,  Rivers State is the epicentre of investments in the country. April 4, 2020 In "News" Britain and the US on Tuesday banned laptops and tablet computers from the passenger compartment of flights from several Middle East and North African nations. March 21, 2017 In "News"